      "role": "user",
      "content": "800mg sounds like a lot though. is it really necessary to take that much all at once? i've only ever taken like 200mg or 400mg before. and honestly i don't really want to go to the doctor if i can help it, it's such a hassle. if i just stick to the ice and rest and take a normal dose of advil, do you think it'll still be okay?",
